### Describe the bug

Hi, I need to use the same partial view twice within my main view and I am trying to set the TemplateInfo.HtmlFieldPrefix property on the ViewDataDictionary in order to keep all of the ID's unique.  The HtmlFieldPrefix is not appended top all partial view ID's as expected.   Please see steps to reproduce below.

### Expected Behavior

All ID's rendered in the partial view should include the prefix set using the TemplateInfo.HtmlFieldPrefix property.

### Steps To Reproduce

@{
    var originalViewData = new ViewDataDictionary(ViewData);
    originalViewData.TemplateInfo.HtmlFieldPrefix = "MySpecialPrefix";
}
@await Html.PartialAsync("_MyModalPopup", Model.MyViewModel, originalViewData)


